N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7901.1 - Purpose and scope

State Regulations

This Part establishes the procedures that govern the
filing and evaluation of applications for assignment of liquid fossil fuels
under the State set-aside program. Notes
